\ 1. type-of consumes its input
5 type-of print
.s empty \ Should show an empty stack

\ 2. Type predicates consume their input
3.14 float? print
.s empty \ Should show an empty stack

\ 3. System words
pwd type-of print \ Should be "string"
.s empty

"whoami" shell swap type-of print drop \ Should be "string"
.s empty
